window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>A standalone enemies to lovers, brother's best friend, arranged marriage, dark mafia romance from USA Today bestselling author, Jane Henry</i></b></p> <p>Semyon Kopolov.<br> Gorgeous and formidable.<br> My childhood crush and brother’s best friend.<br> <br> They call him the Ice King—cold, ruthless, unforgiving.<br> He’s the reason my mother’s dead.<br> <i>Now he’s my husband.</i></p> <p>Once he was my protector.<br> The boy who carried me when I fell and swore to shield me from monsters.<br> <i>Until he became one.</i></p> <p>Forced into marriage, I’m trapped with the man I swear I’ll never forgive.<br> But the harder I try to escape, the harder I fall.<br> My body betrays me, and my heart whispers lies.<br> I tell myself he’s not the boy I once loved,<br> Yet I’m forced to face my greatest fear:<br> I’m falling for my enemy.<i> </i></p>"; 
